{
  "stem": "2118.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then when we were hungry enough to eat it, there wasn't anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my brother, Manny, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from upstairs, you know, he-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he got-- he did something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had a fight with somebody in a line for some oil-- a little oil they were handing out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they arrested him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And once he got arrested, they had already a record.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, in ghetto, there were some disturbances-- like, some strikes or something-- and demonstrations.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm talking about 1940, right after the closing of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they registered the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the Germans came, and they said they need people to go to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in order to supply the people what they needed to work-- let's say they needed 200, 300 people-- they picked the strong arm people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, they knew who the strong arm people from before the war who were-- you know, we used to call them-- it wasn't-- the word wasn't strong arm, but the word was-- well, it would be considered here like a hoodlum.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But hoodlum there and hoodlum here is still a big difference, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have guns or-- or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't kill people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could beat up somebody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they arrested those people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was already arrested by the Jewish Sonderkommando, the Jewish police, inside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They created the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my brother being-- had been in a fight, he was arrested with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was sent away with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1940 or '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am not absolutely sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was in 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he went-- he was sent to a camp, to a working camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
